{"flatpakAppId":"net.sf.imagination.imagination","name":"Imagination","summary":"DVD slide show maker","description":"\n    <p>\n      Imagination is a lightweight and user-friendly DVD slide show maker with  a clean interface and few dependencies.\nIt only requires the ffmpeg encoder  to produce a movie to be burned with another application.    Imagination has the following features:     - Easy to operate.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      - It can make a slideshow from photos selected by user.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      - Support to VOB (DVD Video), OGV (Theora Vorbis), FLV (Flash Video) and 3GP (Mobile Phones) when exporting videos.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      - Support screen resolutions from 128x96 pixels up to 1920x1080 pixels, when exporting videos.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      - Background audio (music, as MP3 files, or other audio files).\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      - Auto resize (optional) for images.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      - Allow the users to select a background color.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      - Over 50 transition effects.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      - Zoom effect with duration time.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      - Allow users to add explanatory texts (e.g. subtitles).    Imagination can be used to make presentations to be\nshown by a projector or  by a smart TV.\n    </p>\n  ","developerName":null,"projectLicense":"GPL-2.0-or-later","homepageUrl":null,"donationUrl":null,"translateUrl":null,"bugtrackerUrl":null,"helpUrl":null,"categories":[{"name":"AudioVideo"}],"downloadFlatpakRefUrl":"imagination","currentReleaseVersion":null,"currentReleaseDescription":null,"iconDesktopUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/jammy/net/sf/imagination.imagination/1edc6a5b0f3286284d10218ccb74a18c/icons/128x128/imagination_imagination.png","iconMobileUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/jammy/net/sf/imagination.imagination/1edc6a5b0f3286284d10218ccb74a18c/icons/128x128/imagination_imagination.png","screenshots":[{"thumbUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/jammy/net/sf/imagination.